snippet.title: Viking Survivors - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Viking Survivors is an action roguelite where you slay hordes of creatures while learning powerful skills to enhance your warrior. Unlock new characters, weapons and abilities. Design the most broken build and slay your enemies before they surround you!

WISHLIST NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2329880/Viking_Survivors/
DISCORD: https://discord.com/invite/DbtDSuxkHx
